import React from "react";
import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom";
import { Navbar, Nav, NavItem } from "reactstrap";
import { frontendUrls } from "../../routes/frontendUrls";

const Header = () => (
    <Navbar color="light" light expand="md" className="d-flex justify-content-center mb-4">
        <Nav className="text-uppercase border">
            <NavItem className="mr-2">
                <NavLink
                    exact
                    to={frontendUrls.home}
                    activeClassName="bg-warning"
                    className="p-3"
                >
                    home
                </NavLink>
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem className="mr-2">
                <NavLink
                    to={frontendUrls.catalogue}
                    activeClassName="bg-warning"
                    className="p-3"
                >
                    catalogue
                </NavLink>
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem className="mr-2">
                <NavLink
                    to={frontendUrls.registration}
                    activeClassName="bg-warning"
                    className="p-3"
                >
                    registration
                </NavLink>
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem className="mr-2">
                <NavLink
                    to={frontendUrls.editProduct}
                    activeClassName="bg-warning"
                    className="p-3"
                >
                    editProduct
                </NavLink>
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem className="mr-2">
                <NavLink
                    to={frontendUrls.addProduct}
                    activeClassName="bg-warning"
                    className="p-3"
                >
                    addProduct
                </NavLink>
            </NavItem>
        </Nav>
    </Navbar>
)

export default Header;
